snippet.title: Myst IV - Revelation Trailer
snippet.description: Trailer for Ubisoft's 2004 PC adventure game Myst IV: Revelation, with music by Jack Wall and Peter Gabriel. Revelation is the sequel to Myst III: Exile (2001).
